rs share  engage with content rd functionality aspnetsessionid session iis session cookie rd strictly necessary fcmtgr session f load balance session cookie rd strictly necessary anonymousidentifier  year stores encrypted data containing anonymous identifier generated by communigator of anonymous website site users st analytics trackingdata  year used for tracking user information of a contact directed to the site from a communigator tracked link stores encrypted data eg campaign identifier contact identifier email address campaign name st performance wowanonymousid  year used to track a visitor uniquely between visits does not identify the user just their visit history so that their website browsing can be joined into a story st performance wowlastvisit min last visit time used for tracking sessions st performance wowsession min id of the session enables tracking of pages viewed during a session not able to track use over multiple visits st performance aspnetsessionid session iis session cookie rd strictly necessary what do cookies do for me ‘strictly necessary’ cookies are essential in order to enable you to move around our website and use its features such as accessing our secure websites without these essential cookies services you have specifically asked for cannot be provided ‘performance cookies’ collect information about how you use our website eg which pages you visit and if you experience any errors all the information collected is used to help us improve how our website works we use analytics cookies in order to collect information about how visitors use the website for instance which pages visitors go to most often and whether any error messages are generated analytics cookies are used to improve the performance of our website ‘functionality’ cookies are used to provide other services such as navigate back to a promotion that might have attracted your attention on your first visit or to remember setting choices you make to improve your visit ‘targeting’ cookies are used to collect information in order to deliver adverts more relevant to you and your interests these cookies also allow you to link to social networking sites such as linkedin what do i need to do the cookie settings on this website are set to ‘allow all cookies’ to improve the overall performance of our website and give you the best user experience if you continue to use our website you consent to us placing cookies on your device and using those cookies as described above and you do not need to do anything further these settings can be changed at any time through our cookie policy at the bottom of our website what if i don’t want cookies to make it easier for you to manage your cookie settings with us we have provided you with the ability to disable some of the cookies we use by unticking this box we will not use the targeting cookies as described above save if you want to disable all cookies by changes to your browser settings please be aware this will make browsing our websites much slower and some of the features described above when using strictly necessary performance and functionality cookies will not be available to you however this is your decision and as such for more information how to control your cookies can be found at httpwwwallaboutcookiesorg and httpwwwyouronlinechoiceseu share this page contact us your recently viewed items you need javascript enabled for us to remember your recently viewed items you might also be interested in unit trust and investment funds visit our investment fund site for retail fund information sicav and oeic funds visit our uk funds section for institutional fund information fund prices the latest prices for lgim funds you are here home cookie policy about us our business history team awards diversity and inclusion our clients events careers fund prices press contact us locations  legal  general investment management holdings limited  all rights reserved lgim accepts no responsibility for the content of any ema